modName: Aados Island - New Lands with Quest W.I.P
summary: Aados island is a new East Empire Company base. The mod currently adds 2 quests and is a W.I.P.
descriptionHtml: Aados island is a new East Empire Company base. The mod currently adds 2 quests, it is a W.I.P and more content will be released in the future. It can be accessed from a ship in Solitude Docks, through a trap door.Aados currently only uses vanilla Skyrim content meaning no DLC or other mods required. This is a really early version so lots more content and improvements to come.
author: Har_j
